<div id="block-views-further-block" class="block block--views block--views-further-block">
        <h2 class="block__title"><span>Further</span></h2>
      <div class="block__content">
    <div class="view view-further view-id-further view-display-id-block view-dom-id-3bca79b313c386afecbfa9a5b927d9c6">
        
  
  
      <div class="view-content">
        <div class="views-row views-row-1 views-row-odd views-row-first views-row-last">
      
  <div class="views-field views-field-field-hp-title">        <div class="field-content"><a href="/further/2019/02/25/moron-only-emergency">This Moron Is the Only Emergency</a></div>  </div>  
  <div class="views-field views-field-field-image">        <div class="field-content"><p class="print-no">
   <a href="/further/2019/02/25/moron-only-emergency"><img class="" src="https://www.commondreams.org/sites/default/files/styles/cd_special_coverage/public/further/china_glasses_reuters_5c744814dda4c82a488b45d0.jpg?itok=u7SNkuXT" width="420" height="220" alt="" /></a></p>
</div>  </div>  
  <div class="views-field views-field-body">        <div class="field-content">Almost 60 former national security officials/grownups have written a letter declaring there is "no emergency that remotely justifies" Trump's move to build a wall. But - breaking news! - there's def an emergency, and he's it. In the last days, he publicly pouted about a term he misunderstood in trade talks, prompting snickering from Chinese officials, then described said officials as "from central casting" with this glasses gesture. Surely slanty eyes are next. Cohen, Mueller, Congress, please...</div>  </div>  
  <div class="views-field views-field-field-more-text">        <div class="field-content"><a href="/further/2019/02/25/moron-only-emergency">Read More...</a></div>  </div>  </div>
    </div>
  
  
  
      
<div class="more-link">
  <a href="https://www.commondreams.org/further">
    More Further  </a>
